  <p>
    A septic service visit goes fastest — and costs least — when the crew can get straight to the tank
    and start working. Most of what slows a visit down is avoidable with a few minutes of preparation
    beforehand. None of it is complicated; it's just the difference between a crew that arrives and
    works and one that arrives and first has to solve a series of access puzzles on your dime.
  </p>

  {/* Intended asset: /images/resources/preparing-a-property-for-septic-service-hero.webp — see public/images/resources/README.md */}
